CatDescriptText: The children's Christmas party at the Gaines Funeral Home on 220 Auburn Street in the East Liberty neighborhood was a major community event.  The man giving away chocolates in the center of the group may be George W. Gaines, proprietor. (from related image 1996.69.333)
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of boys, girls, women, and George Gaines at center, standing in church interior at the Gaines Funeral Home, with Christmas tree in background
